OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,FBritain will make "a wide-ranging
OL,7,Fmilitary contribution" to an
OL,8,Finternational mission to protect
OL,9,Fshipping in the vital Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz, the UK ambassador to the US
OL,11,Fhas said.
OL,13,FThe commitment by Sir Christian Turner
OL,14,Fcomes amid long-running concerns over
OL,15,Fthe state of the nation's armed forces
OL,16,Fand warnings of under-funding.
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,FOnly this week, Labour former defence
OL,7,Fsecretary and Nato chief Lord
OL,8,FRobertson of Port Ellen accused his
OL,9,Fown government of "corrosive
OL,10,Fcomplacency" in the face of "the
OL,11,Fbright red signals of danger".
OL,13,FThe multinational mission, led by the
OL,14,FUK and France, aims to provide
OL,15,Freassurance to vessels using the
OL,16,Fcritical Gulf waterway once the Iran
OL,17,Fconflict is over, Turner told an event
OL,18,Fin Washington.
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@LO]rD@]OUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,FThe initiative was announced at talks
OL,7,Fin Paris involving nearly 50
OL,8,Fcountries, which the top diplomat said
OL,9,Fsignalled global resolve to prevent
OL,10,Ftolls or restrictions being imposed on
OL,11,Fthe Strait of Hormuz.
OL,13,FSo far around 12 nations have
OL,14,Fcommitted to take part.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,FAbout one fifth of the world's oil and
OL,7,Fgas passes through the Strait of
OL,8,FHormuz, of which Iran has staged an
OL,9,Feffective blockade in response to
OL,10,Fairstrikes by the US and Israel,
OL,11,Fforcing up global energy and fuel
OL,12,Fprices.
OL,14,FAfter the US staged a blockade of its
OL,15,Fown of Iran's ports on Monday,
OL,16,FWashington and Tehran both said on
OL,17,FFriday that the strait was "fully
OL,18,Fopen" again to commercial vessels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,FThe blockade of Iran's ports remains
OL,7,Fin place, however, and early on
OL,8,FSaturday Iran's parliamentary speaker
OL,9,FMohammad Bagher Qalibaf posted on X
OL,10,Fthat if the US blockade continued "the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz will not remain open".
OL,13,FUS President Donald Trump derided the
OL,14,Fmultinational mission to secure the
OL,15,Fstrait, using it as a fresh
OL,16,Fopportunity to criticise Nato as
OL,17,F"useless" after it refused to support
OL,18,Fhis offensive against Iran.
OL,26,@rD@cOUsD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,FIn response, Turner pointed out the UK
OL,7,Fand France-led mission was not being
OL,8,Fled by the military alliance.
OL,10,FHe said the planned steps to safeguard
OL,11,Ffuture freedom of navigation would
OL,12,Ffollow "seamlessly" on from the
OL,13,Fannouncement by Iran that it had
OL,14,Freopened the strait to shipping as
OL,15,Fpart of the cessation of hostilities
OL,16,Fin the Middle East.
OL,18,FThe US and Iran are in the middle of a
OL,19,Ffragile truce which is due to last
OL,20,Funtil April 22, while Israel and
OL,21,FLebanon have begun a 10-day ceasefire.
OL,26,@tD@HOUtD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,FAsked by a reporter on Friday night
OL,7,Fwhat he will do if there's no deal
OL,8,Fwhen a ceasefire with Iran expires
OL,9,Fnext week, Trump said: "I don't know.
OL,10,FMaybe I won't extend it, but the
OL,11,Fblockade is going to remain.
OL,13,F"But maybe I won't extend it, so
OL,14,Fyou'll have a blockade and
OL,15,Funfortunately we'll have to start
OL,16,Fdropping bombs again."
OL,18,FHowever, Trump also told reporters
OL,19,Faccompanying him aboard Air Force One
OL,20,Fto Washington that, "I think it's
OL,21,Fgoing to happen," referring to a deal.
OL,26,@qD@XOUuD@AOUxD@VO]|D@UOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,FReferring to Friday's meeting in
OL,7,FParis, Turner said: "The very scale of
OL,8,Fthat 49 country coalition, which
OL,9,Fincluded leaders from Africa, from
OL,10,FAsia, South Korea, Japan, the scale
OL,11,Fand size of it shows the international
OL,12,Fresolve and willingness to act and to
OL,13,Fshow Iran that it is isolated.
OL,15,F"The critical and key message is that
OL,16,Fthere is global agreement that there
OL,17,Fcan be no tolls or restriction on the
OL,18,Fpassage of trade through those through
OL,19,Fthose straits.
OL,26,@oD@UOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,F"And I'm pleased to say that the
OL,7,Fdiscussion, as well as reiterating
OL,8,Fthat resolve was practically
OL,9,Forientated."
OL,11,FHe added: "Military planning is under
OL,12,Fway, and it's focusing on marshalling
OL,13,Fcapabilities to provide reassurance to
OL,14,Fthe shipping industry in the aftermath
OL,15,Fof the ceasefire that we hope is going
OL,16,Fto be cemented and confirmed.
OL,18,F"Specifically, the UK and France have
OL,19,Fagreed that they are establishing an
OL,20,Findependent, multinational mission.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]sD@KOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,F"It will be defensive but protect
OL,7,Fmerchant vessels, reassure commercial
OL,8,Fshipping operators and conduct mine
OL,9,Fclearance operations as soon as
OL,10,Fconditions permit.
OL,12,F" And there are 12 countries of
OL,13,Ftoday's talks who have already offered
OL,14,Fcapabilities for that mission.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,F"The UK itself, will be making a wide-
OL,7,Franging military contribution, and
OL,8,Fthat will be confirmed and announced
OL,9,Fat a military planning conference, to
OL,10,Fin effect bring all of that together
OL,11,Funder a clear command and control
OL,12,Fstructure, that will happen early next
OL,13,Fweek."
