OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,FPressed over Trump's latest criticism
OL,7,Fof Nato, telling it to "stay away",
OL,8,Fthe ambassador made a point of
OL,9,Fpraising the president's leadership in
OL,10,Fdriving up defence spending by members
OL,11,Fwith a recognition that Europe "has to
OL,12,Fburden share".
OL,14,FHe added: "Although Nato was an
OL,15,Fobserver of (the) talks, this is not a
OL,16,FNato mission, because it's a mission
OL,17,Fwe're trying to stand up in the Strait
OL,18,Fof Hormuz".
OL,26,@oD@XOUoD@bO]sD@`OUtD@MO]vD@KOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776553377
OL,3,CUK to make 'wide-ranging military
OL,4,Ccontribution' to Hormuz mission
OL,6,FAt the same time, Turner also stressed
OL,7,Fthe importance of Nato describing it
OL,8,Fas "the most successful and enduring
OL,9,Fdefensive alliance in history".
OL,11,FHe said: "It's not a question of us
OL,12,Fand them. We're all Nato. It's
OL,13,Fsafeguarded Americans and Europeans
OL,14,Ffor over 75 years."
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
